							<pb n="197"/></cell></row></table></p><p><table><row><cell></cell><cell>36. </cell><cell>Dreiviertelkrone, Carmichael </cell><cell>75 </cell><cell>75–130 </cell></row><row><cell></cell><cell>37. </cell><cell>Zahnhalsfüllung </cell><cell>35 </cell><cell>35–55 </cell></row><row><cell></cell><cell></cell><cell>Für größere und komplizierte Füllungen können die Ansätze bis zum doppelten Betrag erhöht werden </cell><cell></cell><cell></cell></row></table></p><p><title>F. Kronen:</title></p><p><table><row><cell></cell><cell>38. </cell><cell>Goldkrone </cell><cell>für Praemolar </cell><cell>65 </cell><cell>65–100 </cell></row><row><cell></cell><cell></cell><cell></cell><cell>– Molar </cell><cell>75 </cell><cell>75–120 </cell></row></table></p><p><table><row><cell></cell><cell>39. </cell><cell>Richmondkrone  </cell><cell>90 </cell><cell>100–140 </cell></row></table></p><p><table><row><cell></cell><cell>40. </cell><cell>Jacketkrone </cell><cell>aus Porzellan </cell><cell>– </cell><cell>130–180 </cell></row><row><cell></cell><cell></cell><cell>– </cell><cell>aus Kunststoff </cell><cell>– </cell><cell>100–150 </cell></row></table></p><p><title>G. Brücken:</title></p><p><table><row><cell></cell><cell>41. </cell><cell>Anker je nach Konstruktion entsprechend Pos. 35–36 und 38–40 </cell><cell>– </cell><cell>– </cell></row></table></p><p><table><row><cell></cell><cell>42. </cell><cell>Zwischenglied </cell><cell>ohne Facette </cell><cell>60 </cell><cell>60–100 </cell></row><row><cell></cell><cell></cell><cell></cell><cell>mit Facette </cell><cell>75 </cell><cell>75–110 </cell></row></table></p><p><table><row><cell></cell><cell>43. </cell><cell>Abnehmen oder Wiederbefestigen einer Krone oder eines Stiftzahnes pro 34 Stunde </cell><cell>5 </cell><cell>6–15 </cell></row><row><cell></cell><cell>44. </cell><cell>Ersatz einer Facette </cell><cell>20 </cell><cell>20–40 </cell></row></table></p><p><title>H. Plattenprothesen:</title></p><p><table><row><cell></cell><cell></cell><cell>a)